channel.title: Files Cfg not found when running server. How to fix that?
channel.description:
I am trying to run my server based of DeltaScape on my iTouch and it works but when I run it, it says: Autospawn.cfg file not found, shops.cfg not found and like three other one. But the problem is that I got all my .cfg file in "config". The file cfg are not saying file not found on my computer. I even tried to put all my config files into my other files and it didnt worked. Can you help me fix that please ? Because I can't see npc or shops if it doesnt work.
Thanks.
